content: I've been eyeing that reclaimed wood coffee table at West Elm, and I think I'll take your advice and check the size and shape to make sure it fits my living room. By the way, do you have any recommendations for some stylish and affordable vases to pair with my new plants? I found a great deal on a pair of high-waisted Levi's jeans at Crossroads Trading Co. recently, and I'm hoping to find a similar steal on a vase.
